add reaction description: <0/> adds a reaction to post <1>{{ postId }}</1> of subspace <2>{{ subspaceId }}</2>
remove reaction description: <0/> removes reaction <1>{{ reactionId }}</1> from post <2>{{ postId }}</2> of subspace <3>{{ subspaceId }}</3>
add registered reaction description: <0/> adds a registered reaction to subspace <1>{{ subspaceId }}</1>
edit registered reaction description: <0/> modifies registered reaction <1>{{ reactionId }}</1> of subspace <2>{{ subspaceId }}</2>
remove registered reaction description: <0/> removes registered reaction <1>{{ reactionId }}</1> from subspace <2>{{ subspaceId }}</2>
set reactions params description: <0/> sets reactions params of subspace <1>{{ subspaceId }}</1>
